{"type": "article", "id": 35652, "title": "这个造型可以调整的边桌，不能更简洁了｜这个设计了不起", "description": "我们每天都为你推荐几个最近发现的好设计。", "date": "2016-12-15T23:33:14Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 271, "name": "工业设计"}, {"id": 35861, "name": "HANKOYA"}, {"id": 35862, "name": "FondForm"}, {"id": 35863, "name": "Genesis Healthcare"}, {"id": 30910, "name": "Taeg Nishimoto"}, {"id": 35864, "name": "大口进也"}], "category": 17, "column": 38, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 130, "image": "img/article/article_show/20161216073256XNYU9CmZ2lsGIuEb.jpg", "contents": "<p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} p.p2 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 32.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636; min-height: 25.0px} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>        <style type=\"text/css\"> p.p1 {margin: 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px 0.0px; line-height: 27.0px; font: 18.0px 'PingFang SC'; color: #363636} span.s1 {font-kerning: none} </style>  </p><p>「这个设计了不起」的微信公众号上线啦，直接搜索「BestDesign」或是「Qthings」就可以订阅，关注我们每日发现的新鲜好设计。</p><h3>HANCODE by HANKOYA</h3><p>在日本，姓氏印章是一件相当重要的日常用品，我们之前还介绍过由它们出演的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/29482.html\">广告</a>。日本最大的印章购物网站 HANKOYA 最近联手日本的 Genesis Healthcare 公司，推出了一个非常特别的定制产品 <a href=\"https://www.hancode.jp/\" rel=\"nofollow\">HANCODE</a>，这款印章由航空级别的钛加工而成，印面的图案则是根据定制人的基因生成的。首先，Genesis Healthcare 旗下的基因分析工具 GeneLife MySelf 2.0 会得出五种属性（分别是社会性、开放性、协调性、勤勉性和慎重纤细性）的数值，代表每个属性的图案会因此产生变化，最后将它们结合在一起就成了独一无二的印面。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215232941Qc4lCdIP9oDLtVer.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215232941qcBw4kRiFQXOu1LP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.390625\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016121523294110bjEA8QudaWpg4Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.152174\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215232941PMCNvSEH27Um5lXj.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.233696\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>Layer side table by Shinya Oguchi</h3><p>日本设计师<a href=\"http://www.shinyashinya.portfoliobox.net/\" rel=\"nofollow\">大口进也</a>在今年东京设计周上公开的 <a href=\"http://www.shinyashinya.portfoliobox.net/sidetable\" rel=\"nofollow\">Layer</a> 是一款造型简洁却不失功能性的边桌，它由两个不同颜色的 U 型边框构成，边框之间通过一根圆柱相连。既可以与地面平行摆放成为一张两层的边桌，又能与地面垂直后通过旋转里面的边框以改变桌子的造型，适用于各种场合。目前它还没有开始销售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233003GevfUgbY65rBJdzI.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233000YE6eawty5JQznbFx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233000FVl2o7BbLhGrxTei.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233001ANHS7ewvPtCo82aJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666406\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233001k8XCl1NPYgE2WFLD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>L0 by Jimin Jeon</h3><p>当你看到图片中的 L0 时，你会不会觉得它更像是一面梳妆镜？这盏简约的台灯是 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/usti0050012\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jimin Jeon</a> 的设计作品，黑色的椭圆形框架中央是一个圆形的 LED 光源，通过下方的灯罩能够进行旋转，从而调整灯光的位置。L0 采用的是簧片开关，它的底座和灯罩都内置了磁铁，只有处于特定位置才能开关。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233057jE0K6bkNO4MDrF1P.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.562500\" data-format=\"gif\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612152330578V2jZB75ySdentcA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233057CLBz4Z6E7uskdUKe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233056D2GJ4e7UOxfStKzB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612152330581XzHATMGC9tYKjN4.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233056eNCHbglLwdShWIOc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.707500\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>LIQUID by Taeg Nishimoto</h3><p>日本设计师 <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/taegnishimoto\" rel=\"nofollow\">Taeg Nishimoto</a> 利用混凝土和色素制作了这张名为 <a href=\"http://cargocollective.com/taegnishimoto/LIQUID\" rel=\"nofollow\">LIQUID</a> 的墙面镜，看起来脏兮兮的表面是它的一大特色。加工过程本身就像是在创作一幅独特的圆月画作：将事先处理好的圆镜放入模具后，掺有黑色颜料的混凝土按照所含颜料的多少以从大到小的顺序倒入。由于倒入的角度和位置都会影响最终的图案，每一面镜子也因此独一无二。混凝土盘的底部还附带了一个可以旋转的底座，随时改变它的装饰效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233120SRHEI86QGOBLYTNr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201612152331206JDvIjEmBzf35Xg7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.652000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233121nkLplIXPjuDO82Tq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233120bJXUTEuapxLdsF58.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.670000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233121sx6BL2J3SArybM5P.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.656000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>F_Hair Dryer by FondForm</h3><p>来自韩国 <a href=\"http://www.fondform.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">FondForm</a> 工作室的设计师发现，市面上的吹风机造型似乎都大同小异，一旦举着的时间稍长可能会感到手腕不适，而且不使用时该如何收纳电线也是不少人的困扰。最近，他们带来了这款名为 <a href=\"http://www.fondform.com/hair-dryer\" rel=\"nofollow\">F_</a> 的吹风机概念产品，它的顶部是一个可以伸缩、转动的管道，收回的状态下看上去就像是一个黑色的保温杯。除了灵活调整的出风口之外，吹风机的底部也为电线预留了一个小口，可以以两种方式摆放。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233138fowbHUV0LkBRNGmW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233138TB3VE1NxF7mJqKCA.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.830476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233138BJ2KUi8aYMPAeuE6.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.728571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233138NHskJitMwCWK56dv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.703810\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><h3>BobbleKat Fountain by Pauline Dziama et al.</h3><p>来自美国罗切斯特理工学院的几名学生为独自在家的喵星人设计了一个可以玩的水盆 <a href=\"https://www.behance.net/gallery/45242333/BobbleKat-Fountain\" rel=\"nofollow\">BobbleKat Fountain</a>，它的造型或许会让你想到那些猫咪们聚在一起舔冰球的视频。（其实现在也有类似的设计）</p><p>水盆里的球体内置了感应器、水泵以及电池，底部和与它配套的垫子都配有线圈，可以为电池充电。一旦它感应到猫咪过来喝水，它就会将水引导至球体顶端，顺着表面流下供猫咪饮用。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233154CkfcjFweghLvtYbo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665714\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233154Cr0ot7yHGIg5OMKW.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233154UzkWDoVOulJBI2K0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233154Qejmy9T1LJoUOMpN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.998095\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233154s1tAVNEpcQweF67B.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.667619\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\" class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20161215233154ojeImCyq3tiR1QlH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.845714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>"}